# Tauri sidecar binaries.
#
# This directory is populated at build time by
# `src-tauri/scripts/fetch-rwkv-sidecar.sh` with files matching the
# Tauri externalBin naming convention (`<name>-<target-triple>`).
#
# Do not commit the binaries themselves — they are produced by
# `.github/workflows/build-rwkv-sidecar-macos.yml` and shipped via
# tagged GitHub releases. See
# `docs/engineering/plans/2026-05-13-macos-rwkv-one-click-implementation.md`
# Phase 2.
